授認為農業發展為「產業化」的先決條件，而隨著經濟的發展，「產業化」
反過來將翻轉傳統農業（即生產型農業）。試加以申論之。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:55+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "842662bc8124", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110090", "c": "334", "s": "2401", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "農業發展與政策", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "農業行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-444ca548-moex-00214', 'heelevel3-444ca548', 'heelevel3-444ca548-moex-110-c707a372', 'sub-heelevel3-444ca548-03', NULL, 'essay', '老王豆漿店去年出售豆漿的收入為 140 萬元，而支出的費用包括工資
